data.description: Discover the perfect blend of residential comfort and commercial potential in this 5-bedroom, 2-full bath property in the heart of Jourdanton. Only 45 short minutes from San Antonio, sprawling across 1.2870 acres and commercially zoned, this spacious home caters to families and entrepreneurs alike. With ample room for growth, a generous floorplan, and a lush backyard, it offers all the comforts of a family home; meanwhile, its strategic location and commercial zoning make it an ideal choice for those seeking business opportunities. Embrace the charm and practicality of the classic kitchen; with neutral tones, timeless cabinets, and a cozy nook, this space offers vintage elegance and efficiency. The living and dining area blend together seamlessly, allowing for prime entertaining and relaxation. All bedrooms are well appointed, spacious and offer ample storage space. With a multitude of outside access points, this property offers the perfect blend of convenience and flexibility. Additional features including a large detached carport, parking lot, multiple storage sheds and two fully fenced in yards, this property is full of opportunities. Whether you're looking for a cozy family home or the ideal foundation for your next business venture - this versatile property offers the opportunity to unlock endless potential!
